Package: rtortilla
Type: Package
Title: Wrap selected text with a function (or tortilla)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Ben",
           family = "Toh",
           role = c("cre", "aut"),
           email = "kokbent@yahoo.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1371-817X"))
Description: Add an addin to the Rstudio, and you can assign the
    addin with a shortcut key so when you need to wrap a something
    into a function, you can just invoke the shortcut, type the
    function you want and the addin do the job for you.
